Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.94,0:01:36.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,You said it yourself that day: \N“Take apart a Simoun.”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,The only thing that’s in there is a helix.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:43.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,All we can understand about it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:48.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}do{\i0} see something! \NWhat? What are you seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:58.01,Titles,,90,0,0,,{\blur0.6}One By One
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.79,0:02:24.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’re those for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.20,0:02:27.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m collecting them to make a cradle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,A cradle?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.06,0:02:33.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,Back where I grew up, we always used to put out cradles in the springtime.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:38.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,They’re an offering to grant peaceful rest to the souls of those who died before their time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:48.14,Regular,,0,0,0,,That one’s too thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:51.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,How is Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:58.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t know what could have left her in that state, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:00.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, it would be good\N for you to stay by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:02.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:06.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Out of all of us,\N you’re the one closest to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:17.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, did anything happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:35.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.41,0:03:38.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,We were unable to find\N the enemy base ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:40.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t know why they’ve gone, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:41.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Nothing else happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:43.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:46.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:51.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,C’mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:15.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tell me, what was it that Dominura saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:22.86,Regular,,0,0,0,,We should not have \Ntouched such sacred things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,I should not have touched them…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:42.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,As you wish. I’ll never let\N you touch them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:04:59.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s warm…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:04.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,You should rest till tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:07.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Since Dominura is…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:11.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.16,0:05:18.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,What’s happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:21.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’ve sighted the enemy at 11 o’clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:23.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,They don’t seem to be attacking, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.76,0:05:25.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,And Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.46,0:05:28.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,I regret to say that \Nshe remains indisposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:29.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.19,0:05:33.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.76,0:05:45.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let’s go, Neviril!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:46.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:50.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril is exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:52.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,She’s in no condition\N to pray right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:53.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:58.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,With Dominura unable to pray as well, for now you’ll be taking orders from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:00.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,“Orders?”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s like we’re in the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.13,0:06:10.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:21.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,We’re only continuing our reconnaissance. There’s no reason for Neviril to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:22.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,— Kaimu!\N— Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.90,0:06:46.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can’t believe Aaeru \Njust gave up back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was quite taken aback by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.99,0:06:52.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in the past she’d’ve dragged her off by the hand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bleah! I don’t want \Nto see Aaeru like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:58.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.82,0:07:01.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,She’s cool because she’s so positive that it’s overbearing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.60,0:07:04.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Being so weirdly considerate… \Nit’s totally not like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.69,0:07:08.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:10.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.72,0:07:12.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t feel that way about Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:15.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh, Limone, where’s Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:18.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hmm? I just saw her go outside, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Outside, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:22.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder what she could be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.80,0:07:28.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:30.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don’t get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:33.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking that \NI’d take a shower or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,No one asked you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:42.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sheesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:09.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.86,0:08:11.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are you apologizing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.41,0:08:12.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:15.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don’t even know\N why you’re apologizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.08,0:08:17.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re just bowing\N your head for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:18.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I do have a reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:24.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s my fault that you’re feeling bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:28.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don’t understand why, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:32.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just know it’s because of me. So—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:33.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don’t you dare be so conceited!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:54.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.47,0:08:56.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was {\i1}so{\i0} uncool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please forgive my impertinence, Sibylla Aurea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.97,0:09:02.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was insolent of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:15.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,They are the same…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.06,0:09:20.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Amuria and that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:22.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,She was never looking at {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:25.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:29.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru made me see the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,To both of them I am just…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:43.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just a tool. A tool to take them “higher.”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:45.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:54.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,I think… I’ve made a big mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.74,0:10:00.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I were with you—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:05.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m not the person you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.02,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:10.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you say what I think\N you’re going to…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.30,0:10:14.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,…then I know…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:17.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,…that my shell will break.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re very tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:29.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re not really yourself right now. So—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:30.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:35.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,How could I say such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.69,0:10:38.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:39.45,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.45,0:10:40.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.18,0:10:54.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:55.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, you mustn’t!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:10:58.08,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:04.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:07.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,The air around here really stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,The air?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.81,0:11:12.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is that okay, Alti?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:14.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, if Floe really wants to…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:18.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Mamiina, Rodoreamon, back them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:19.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:38.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.50,0:11:42.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yun and the others \Nhaven’t come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:46.40,Regular,,0,0,0,,The enemy isn’t attacking, so to just go out without a plan like that—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:48.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you saying I made a bad decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:51.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I didn’t say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.89,0:12:02.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can’t always be by your side,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:05.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,but I can still try to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:07.92,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:50.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,Quiet, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:55.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re not going to go \Nlook at the Simoun today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.00,0:12:58.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, wanna play hide-and-seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:05.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s kid stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.59,0:13:06.89,Regular,,0,0,0,,How about it, Aaeru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.89,0:13:08.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sure! Sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:14.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,All right, Morinas, count to a hundred!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:16.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don’t be cheating on us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.20,0:13:18.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:24.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,1… 2… 3… 4… 5…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:23.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hide, Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.19,0:13:28.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,6… 7… 8… 9… 10…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.08,0:14:22.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,That song…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:26.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s the same as Aaeru’s music box!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:28.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,“The Door to a New World.”
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:29.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:33.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,It’s the song of the migrants,\N who were searching for a land of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.85,0:14:46.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Tempus Spatium took us in when \Nwe had been wandering without rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:52.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Chor Dextra was created to perform the Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:56.91,Regular,,0,0,0,,We were warriors chosen in the knowledge that we would die…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.62,Regular,,0,0,0,,…and I was fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:04.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,In exchange for my death,\N the Holy Land gave my life meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.74,0:15:06.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:10.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,I always have. Always!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:13.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,That’s why…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:15.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,You are needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.94,0:15:19.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to do the Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.26,0:15:21.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to do it with you, Dominura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because… you’re my pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:47.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Paraietta!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:48.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,The rain is getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:51.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, come back inside \Nbefore it affects your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:33.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Do you need to talk to Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:42.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.63,0:16:52.82,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why am I so indecisive?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.58,Regular,,0,0,0,,When I’m like this, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:55.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.72,0:17:33.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know, this is {\i1}very{\i0} weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:37.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Maybe it’s better to wait\N until Dominura comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:40.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you saying we can’t do anything without her giving instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is no time to be petty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:45.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,“Petty,” you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.75,0:17:48.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know, if we keep on like this…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.21,0:17:49.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:55.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,You’re going to pair with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:56.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.93,0:17:58.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,You and I are going to go \Non a reconnaissance mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,— And from now on—\N— No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:01.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’ll be the one to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.97,0:18:04.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.99,0:18:07.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Morinas, you’re with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.25,0:18:09.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:11.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,Neviril, no! You’re still—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:15.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Please, let me go, Paraietta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.56,0:18:51.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,I’m…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:53.90,Regular,,0,0,0,,worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.45,0:19:30.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should we do about our game?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.99,0:19:40.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,She’s going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:43.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:44.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:50.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those are the eyes \Nof someone who’s about to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:53.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:13.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:25.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura, I want to hear\N your advice on this matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.85,0:20:27.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,What do you think \Nabout the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:35.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:39.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.88,0:20:48.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is your judgement so unreliable that you’d rather listen to someone who’s been asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:04.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:06.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,More, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.44,0:21:22.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Emerald Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:26.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,By dismantling the Simoun,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:30.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,I feel as though I saw what lies beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:36.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,But you don’t know if you really saw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:40.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,Until you actually do it,\N you won’t know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.45,0:21:45.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,It certainly seems like it, doesn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.03,0:21:51.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were always told \Nto fly higher, weren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:55.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,To draw Ri Maajons in the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.01,0:22:00.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,So to deny you that would be \Nto deny you your very self.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.49,0:22:08.03,Regular,,0,0,0,,You know, we’re so much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:10.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,I chose you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.38,0:22:12.32,Regular,,0,0,0,,and you chose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.90,0:22:16.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,That connection is what\N creates the Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.76,0:22:21.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just for you, I want to draw…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.94,0:22:31.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,…the Emerald Ri Maajon.
